      <h2 class="heading-2">FTMO Payouts & Profit Split</h2>
      <p class="body-large">
        FTMO has an industry-leading reputation for fast, reliable payouts. Over $200 million paid to traders and counting.
      </p>

      <div class="payout-highlights">
        <div class="payout-card">
          <div class="payout-value">80%</div>
          <div class="payout-label">Starting Profit Split</div>
          <p>Keep 80% of all profits from day one as a funded trader.</p>
        </div>
